The '''Friends of Paran''' were a resistance group on [[Derilyn]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. The [[Protocol droid/Legends|protocol]] [[Droid/Legends|droid]] [[N2-3P0|N2-3PO]] was a member.

After contact with the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Alliance to Restore the Republic]] via the [[Smuggler/Legends|smuggler]] [[Shondra Del]], the Friends of Paran took into consideration aligning with the Alliance.

